==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hunky
<hw>Hunk"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Perh. fr.
<er>Hunk</er>.]</ety> <def>All right; in a good condition; also, even;
square.</def> <mark>[Slang, U. S.]</mark><-- hunky dory? --></p>

<p><q>He . . . began to shoot; began to get
⟦ldquo⟧<qex>hunky</qex>⟦rdquo⟧ with all those people who had been
plugging at him.</q> <rj><qau>Stephen Crane.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hunnemannia</ent>⟦br⟧
